20,1,$1+$1,$4,$5,$6,$7,0*
20,1,$1+$1,$6,$7,$8,$9,0*
20,1,$1+$1,$8,$9,$2,$3,0*%
%AMRotRect*
0 Rectangle, with rotation*
0 The origin of the aperture is its center*
0 $1 length*
0 $2 width*
